text: Taina Kolkkala in Kalevan kisat 2008 Taina Maria Kolkkala, née Uppa (born 24 October 1976 in Pori) is a retired female javelin thrower from Finland. Her personal best is 64.06 metres, achieved in July 2000 in Pihtipudas.
